"title": "5017: heart, results of renewal in",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "5017",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>An individual, if renewed and led by the Holy Spirit, will be aware of new spiritual experiences and desires, and also of the Holy Spirit's work of restoring character. These things provide evidence of the grace of God at work in the life of a believer.</p>\n<h2>Inward experiences of the renewed heart</h2>\n<h3>Assurance</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John3:19-1John3:21\">1JN 3:19–3:21</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps112:7-Ps112:8\">PSA 112:7–112:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:14-Rom8:16\">ROM 8:14–8:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph1:18-Eph1:19\">EPH 1:18–1:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John5:10\">1JN 5:10</a></p>\n<h3>Love for God's word</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom7:22\">ROM 7:22</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut4:9\">DEU 4:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps37:31\">PSA 37:31</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:11\">PSA 119:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:30\">PSA 119:30</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:111\">PSA 119:111</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov6:21\">PRO 6:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer15:16\">JER 15:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer31:33\">JER 31:33</a></p>\n<h3>Desire for holiness</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt5:8\">MAT 5:8</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr17:6\">2CH 17:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps19:14\">PSA 19:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps24:3-Ps24:4\">PSA 24:3–24:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps73:1\">PSA 73:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov7:25\">PRO 7:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl10:2\">ECC 10:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col3:1-Col3:2\">COL 3:1–3:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim2:22\">2TI 2:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet3:15\">1PE 3:15</a>DEU <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet10:16\">10:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer4:4\">JER 4:4</a></p>\n<h3>Desire to seek God</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs8:38-1Kgs8:39\">1KI 8:38–8:39</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:10\">PSA 119:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:58\">PSA 119:58</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:145\">PSA 119:145</a></p>\n<h3>Encouragement</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps27:14\">PSA 27:14</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr16:9\">2CH 16:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps73:26\">PSA 73:26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer51:46\">JER 51:46</a>JHN <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer14:1\">14:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John14:27\">JHN 14:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col3:15\">COL 3:15</a>\n<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor4:1\">2CO 4:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor4:14\">2CO 4:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil4:7\">PHP 4:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col2:2\">COL 2:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col4:8\">COL 4:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phlm1:20\">PHM 1:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb12:3\">HEB 12:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb12:5\">HEB 12:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb13:9\">HEB 13:9</a></p>\n<h3>Joy</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps105:3\">PSA 105:3</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr16:10\">1CH 16:10</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs8:66\">1KI 8:66</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr7:10\">2CH 7:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps4:7\">PSA 4:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps16:9\">PSA 16:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa65:14\">ISA 65:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zeph3:14\">ZEP 3:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke24:32\">LUK 24:32</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts2:46-Acts2:47\">ACT 2:46–2:47</a></p>\n<h3>Desire for the salvation of others</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom9:1-Rom9:3\">ROM 9:1–9:3</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom10:1\">ROM 10:1</a></p>\n<h3>Various kinds of distress</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps143:4\">PSA 143:4</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps38:8\">PSA 38:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps69:20\">PSA 69:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer4:19\">JER 4:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer8:18-Jer8:19\">JER 8:18–8:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer23:9\">JER 23:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lam1:20\">LAM 1:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lam2:11\">LAM 2:11</a>ACT <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lam21:13\">21:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor2:4\">2CO 2:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil3:18\">PHP 3:18</a></p>\n<h3>Love for the church</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet1:22\">1PE 1:22</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech7:10\">ZEC 7:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John13:14-John13:15\">JHN 13:14–13:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts4:32\">ACT 4:32</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor6:11-2Cor6:13\">2CO 6:11–6:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor7:2-2Cor7:3\">2CO 7:2–7:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil1:7-Phil1:9\">PHP 1:7–1:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim1:5\">1TI 1:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John3:11-1John3:18\">1JN 3:11–3:18</a></p>\n<h2>The renewed heart and the restoration of character</h2>\n<h3>Sincerity and integrity towards God and other people</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps86:11\">PSA 86:11</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs3:6\">1KI 3:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs9:4\">1KI 9:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job33:3\">JOB 33:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps15:2\">PSA 15:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps78:72\">PSA 78:72</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt18:35\">MAT 18:35</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor5:12\">2CO 5:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph6:5-Eph6:6\">EPH 6:5–6:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col3:22-Col3:23\">COL 3:22–3:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas4:8\">JAS 4:8</a></p>\n<h3>Humility</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps131:1\">PSA 131:1</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut8:14\">DEU 8:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs22:19\">2KI 22:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr32:25-2Chr32:26\">2CH 32:25–32:26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt5:3\">MAT 5:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil2:3-Phil2:5\">PHP 2:3–2:5</a></p>\n<h3>Wisdom</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov2:10\">PRO 2:10</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job38:36\">JOB 38:36</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps90:12\">PSA 90:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov2:2\">PRO 2:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov3:1\">PRO 3:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov3:3\">PRO 3:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov23:15\">PRO 23:15</a></p>\n<h2>The possibility of the renewed heart becoming faithless</h2>\n<h3>The importance of self-examination before God</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps139:23-Ps139:24\">PSA 139:23–139:24</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut8:2\">DEU 8:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut13:3\">DEU 13:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg5:15-Judg5:16\">JDG 5:15–5:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam16:7\">1SA 16:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr28:9\">1CH 28:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr32:31\">2CH 32:31</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps7:9\">PSA 7:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps26:2\">PSA 26:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov17:3\">PRO 17:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer20:12\">JER 20:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts1:24\">ACT 1:24</a></p>\n<h3>Backsliding</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos5:4\">HOS 5:4</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs11:4\">1KI 11:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs11:9\">1KI 11:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps78:8\">PSA 78:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps78:37\">PSA 78:37</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa29:13\">ISA 29:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa57:11\">ISA 57:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer12:2\">JER 12:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos10:2\">HOS 10:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mal2:2\">MAL 2:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts5:3\">ACT 5:3</a></p>\n<h3>Restoration after backsliding</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Joel2:12-Joel2:13\">JOL 2:12–2:13</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut4:29\">DEU 4:29</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut30:2-Deut30:3\">DEU 30:2–30:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh24:23\">JOS 24:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs8:46-1Kgs8:51\">1KI 8:46–8:51</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps51:10\">PSA 51:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa57:15\">ISA 57:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer3:17\">JER 3:17</a></p>",
